summary: You think the beggars on the streets are the most awful misery in the towns of Skyrim? Now you got access to the place where the scum really lives.
descriptionHtml: It\'s a dungeon where a few poor people (also children) live. The trapdoor to this place is on the wall next to the stairs of the Windhelm graveyard. There\'s a little shop, a few people, few sleeping and living places, a guard and a statue of Nocturnal in there.
author: LadyMassaca
